abstract: GREENLAWN, L. I., Sept. 28 -- They colored it gold at the Suffolk County Kennel Club's 30th annual dog show today at the Greenlawn Recreation Center. A golden retriever, Ch. Cragmount's Hi-Lo, owned by Mrs. Charles W. Engelhard of Far Hills, N. J., was best in show in an entry limited to 1000.
